Lake House—- steps away from the lake, surrounded by 3 private lakes in Sussex NJ — Great for Flip, live-in or airbnb, just a few miles from popular ski areas 4bed 2bath $180,000

1. Establish Business Entity 
2. Open business bank account for your LLC/SP
3. Deposit all of your earnings 80% to checking, 20% to savings. DO NOT TOUCH YOUR SAVINGS
4. Gather all your bank statements, see accountant, file yearly taxes claiming your actual profit, no losses! You have to show the government you make enough money to afford a house. 
5. You will owe the IRS. You will get a tax bill. Use your savings to pay off IRS. 
6. Do steps 1-5 for 2️⃣ Years. 
7. Contact @homeloansbytone get preapproval, then I can find you a house 🏠
